readable.content: A child leaping from bed to bed behind the back of a man . A man is standing with his arms folded looking at something while the person behind him is jumping onto one of the two beds in the room . a man wearing a yellow shirt standing in the middle of two beds that a boy is jumping on in the background A young child jumping on the bed as a man looks the other way .
